WorkItem.Description:
The classes HorizontalLine and VerticalLine are using the wrong coordinate system. You don't notice it until you have a DataTransform at the Plotter.
Instead of:
Point p1 = new Point(Value, Plotter.Viewport.Visible.YMin).DataToScreen(transform);
Point p2 = new Point(Value, Plotter.Viewport.Visible.YMax).DataToScreen(transform);
it should be something like:
Point p1 = new Point(Value, Plotter.Viewport.Visible.ViewportToData(transform).YMin).DataToScreen(transform);
Point p2 = new Point(Value, Plotter.Viewport.Visible.ViewportToData(transform).YMax).DataToScreen(transform);
